spec_data.Name: texlive-ticollege
spec_data.Description:
This package provides commands to draw scientific calculator
keys with the help of TikZ. It also provides commands to draw
the content of screens and of menu items.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 08:18:30 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Graphical representation of keys on a standard scientific calculator
